eed4e83d272bce20d20411edc","tid":688076,"uid":119393,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b8ebdd327edc359729d0536f551c7ba053fcb095","tid":688076,"uid":38049,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T23:59:13.000Z","msg":"篇嘢好似無講咩人偷捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"GOOGLE鰻魚苗 and 中國人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"點解有人負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a824aefdc8fa1e2c108f6663a569c0d18f23fa8b","tid":688076,"uid":38049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"走私逾百噸極危歐洲鰻苗赴華　不法集團獲利3.5億港元<br />\n05月07日(一) 17:49更新 05:15建立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/mobile/bknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180507%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html&d=sep4BxJtrPbtyNyJ4MjhjVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=003ee1b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/mobile/bknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n東亞地區的的鰻魚幼苗嚴重歉收，有不法商人看準商機，將被國際自然保護聯盟（IUCN）列為極危物種的歐洲鰻魚魚苗，經由西班牙、摩洛哥等地運往中國，輾轉經香港再流入日本市場。在過去數過月內，走私鰻魚魚苗的數量已高達100噸，獲利3750萬歐元（約3.5億港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n西班牙政府上月破獲一個走私鰻魚苗集團，<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕10名來自西班牙、中國及摩洛哥的人</span>。當局在南部港口一輛汽車上，發現原定運往摩洛哥的129公斤鰻魚苗；之後又在該集團於阿爾赫西拉斯的據點，發現裝有逾300公斤鰻魚苗的養殖池，及搬運鰻魚苗用的364個箱。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，該集團把從西班牙收集的鰻魚苗，經由葡萄牙、摩洛哥走私至中國。當局表示，鰻苗最終目的地是亞洲，特別是日本。暫時未知中國將活鰻苗運至日本，抑或是在養殖或加工後運送；西班牙當局形容，「有像黑社會般的網絡在供應歐洲鰻魚」。 <br />\n<br />\n歐洲刑警組織估計，在去年11月至今年3月間，歐洲向中國走私的鰻苗達100噸。歐洲鰻魚保護團體「SEG」指，整個歐盟地區一季漁期能捕獲的131噸鰻苗中，逾半是偷捕而來，而偷捕鰻苗和近半合法捕獲量，則被送至亞洲。SEG呼籲為日本等國合作，杜絕歐洲鰻苗走私活動。"},{"pid":"ff241980aaa1091408e2bf403437a038eb441ac7","tid":688076,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"一睇個post 第一時間諗起中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a3c709d5065d4ec6d17015ef298bea556c0cb7","tid":688076,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"走私逾百噸極危歐洲鰻苗赴華　不法集團獲利3.5億港元<br />\n05月07日(一) 17:49更新 05:15建立<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/mobile/bknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180507%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html&d=sep4BxJtrPbtyNyJ4MjhjVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=003ee1b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180507/mobile/bknint-20180507051548258-0507_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"77b85bdd191319badd34da5a8dec9632681d5803","tid":688076,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來又係班支那狗偷捕/走私魚苗<br />\n之後扮合法野賣比日本養殖場<br />\n<br />\n生態災難去到邊都搵到支那人"},{"pid":"d016d09fc95f5c52e8cea270d205161b72f47c62","tid":688076,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61200d4f6c4cad3ba9cc1b82267e0f0f7e1c37ae","tid":688076,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0974f507e62c212cbec86a113177cf1a8fb6cb","tid":688076,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}